{
  "stem": "24195.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arno, yeah-- my-- his, his name was Arno, A-R-N-O Sommerfeld.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's my mother's name-- maiden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was an actor and a playwright.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a pacifist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it goes without saying that he was a anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, and he was-- my mother was always telling me that my father was standing in front of the television set--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not television.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in front of the radio when Hitler was giving one of his five-hour rambling talks, where he was saying nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was lambasting and attacking the Jews and, and holding them responsible for Germany's miseries and depression.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, according to what my mother told me, was standing in front of the radio and was holding his sides and laughing himself senseless, and saying, the man is an idiot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, he's never going to do that, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's impossible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's, he's kidding, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- while my uncle was saying to him, Ernst, take your family, transfer all your money, and go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the nearest country where you're going to be OK, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many others have done it-- did it, of course, at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And not only going to Switzerland, but they went to England, to the United States, Canada, and Australia, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that-- he would not listen to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother wanted to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, she was afraid because she could see already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, a, a, a government that is-- authorities that are capable of making them be divorced because they're Jewish, what would be their next step, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That would be much more drastic than what they have-- what they're doing now-- what they-- at the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
